@startuml poc_activity
title OpenSDLC PoC — 파이프라인 액티비티 다이어그램

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #EBF5FB
  BorderColor #2980B9
  DiamondBackgroundColor #FDEBD0
  DiamondBorderColor #E67E22
  ArrowColor #2C3E50
  FontSize 12
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #F9A825
}

start

:사용자 입력 수신\n(--user-story, --pipeline);

:pipeline YAML 로드\n(PipelineDefinition 파싱);

:LangGraph 그래프 빌드\n(build_graph_from_definition);
note right
  각 step → node 생성
  ValidatorAgent → conditional edge
  기타 → simple edge
end note

:PipelineState 초기화\n{user_story, iteration_count=0,\n latest_artifacts={}, steps_completed=[]};

== Phase 1: Requirements Analysis ==

:ReqAgent 호출\n[독립 LLM API 호출];
note right
  system_prompt: req-agent.md
               + constitution
               + UC 템플릿
  user_message: User Story (최초)
               또는 이전 UC + fail 사유 (재작업)
end note

:UseCaseModelArtifact (YAML) 생성;
:latest_artifacts["UseCaseModelArtifact"] 갱신;

:ValidatorAgent 호출\n[독립 LLM API 호출 — context 격리!];
note right
  user_message: UC artifact YAML만 전달
  (ReqAgent의 사고 과정, system_prompt 미포함)
end note

:ValidationReportArtifact 생성\n(pass | warning | fail);

if (validation_result == "pass"?) then (YES)
else (NO: fail/warning)
  if (iteration_count >= max_iterations?) then (YES: 한계 초과)
    #Pink:파이프라인 강제 종료\n(pipeline_status = "max_retries_exceeded");
    stop
  else (NO: 재작업 가능)
    :iteration_count++;
    note left: ReqAgent로 루프백
    backward: ReqAgent 재호출\n(이전 UC + fail 사유 포함);
  endif
endif

== Phase 2: Test Design ==

:TestAgent 호출 (mode=design)\n[독립 LLM API 호출];
note right
  user_message: UC artifact YAML
  output: TestDesignArtifact
end note

:TestDesignArtifact (YAML) 생성;

:ValidatorAgent 호출\n(TestDesign 검증);

if (validation_result == "pass"?) then (YES)
else (NO)
  if (iteration_count >= max_iterations?) then (YES)
    #Pink:파이프라인 강제 종료;
    stop
  else (NO)
    :iteration_count++;
    backward: TestAgent 재호출;
  endif
endif

== Phase 3: Implementation ==

:CodeAgent 호출\n[독립 LLM API 호출];
note right
  user_message: UC artifact + TestDesign artifact
  max_tokens: 16384
  output: ImplementationArtifact (YAML + 실제 코드)
end note

:ImplementationArtifact (YAML) 생성;

:ValidatorAgent 호출\n(Implementation 검증);

if (validation_result == "pass"?) then (YES)
else (NO)
  if (iteration_count >= max_iterations?) then (YES)
    #Pink:파이프라인 강제 종료;
    stop
  else (NO)
    :iteration_count++;
    backward: CodeAgent 재호출;
  endif
endif

== Phase 4: Test Execution ==

:TestAgent 호출 (mode=execution)\n[독립 LLM API 호출];
note right
  user_message: TestDesign + Implementation artifact
  output: TestReportArtifact
end note

:TestReportArtifact (YAML) 생성;

:ValidatorAgent 호출\n(TestReport 검증);

if (validation_result == "pass"?) then (YES)
else (NO)
  if (iteration_count >= max_iterations?) then (YES)
    #Pink:파이프라인 강제 종료;
    stop
  else (NO)
    :iteration_count++;
    backward: TestAgent 재호출 (execution);
  endif
endif

== Phase 5: Feedback ==

:CoordAgent 호출\n[독립 LLM API 호출];
note right
  user_message: TestReport artifact
  output: FeedbackArtifact
end note

:FeedbackArtifact (YAML) 생성;

== 산출물 저장 ==

:steps_completed → iteration별 그룹화;

:output/iteration-N/artifacts/*.yaml 저장;

:ImplementationArtifact에서\n실행 코드 파일 추출;

:output/workspace/ 에 코드 파일 저장;

#LightGreen:파이프라인 완료\n(pipeline_status = "completed");

stop

@enduml
